<typeStatus pageId="29" pageNumber="26">allotype</typeStatus>
are in 
<collectionCode box="[1453,1573,1010,1047]" collectionName="MHNP" pageId="29" pageNumber="26">MHNP</collectionCode>
. The 
<typeStatus box="[1707,1850,1010,1047]" pageId="29" pageNumber="26">holotype</typeStatus>
was collected by 
<collectorName box="[1289,1391,1056,1093]" pageId="29" pageNumber="26">Simon</collectorName>
in 
<collectingDate box="[1456,1529,1056,1093]" pageId="29" pageNumber="26">1888</collectingDate>
. The allotype and two paratypes are simply labelled &quot;Novo Gren.&quot; [Colombia], and two other paratypes are labelled &quot;Colomb. Orient.&quot; Four paratypes: MHNP, 2; USNM, 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1852,1885,1193,1230]" pageId="29" pageNumber="26">2.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</materialsCitation>
